olive oil
½ lemon
1 tomato
1 cucumber
1 packet lamb mince
1 sachet chermoula spice blend
6 Mini Flour Tortillas
1 bag Deluxe Salad Mix
1 packet garlic aioli
1 packet Chargrilled Capsicum Relish
1 packet roasted almonds
1 bag parsley

• Heat olive oil in a frying pan over high heat
• Cook beef and seasoning, breaking up with a spoon, until browned, 3-4 mins. Season to taste

• Heat olive oil in a frying pan over high heat
• Cook lamb and seasoning, breaking up with a spoon, until browned, 3-4 mins. Season to taste

• Microwave tortillas on a plate in 10 second bursts, until warmed through. Chop almonds if preferred
• In a bowl, combine salad mix, tomato, cucumber, a squeeze of lemon and a drizzle of oil. Season
• Spread tortillas with aioli, then fill with beef and salad
• Top with capsicum relish, almonds and torn parsley